Umm, the nerf hits druid CoT pets as well, the druid community is pretty pissed about it as well.  Actually, one could argue this hurts druids worse than 'chanters.  Why?  Because 'chanters can charm any 'ole mob in the zone, their pets are far more expendable, can't haste it so now it dies within a few fights?  So what, grab another one.  There's a far smaller base of mobs for a druid to charm, a druid's pet isn't as expendable.  So 'ya gotta heal them, big mana drain there made palatable by being able to haste the pet so it can &quot;process&quot; the mob faster.  No haste on the pet = FAR less efficiency for the druid.  No haste on a 'chanter pet does equal less efficiency as well, but they don't need to save the pet, there's a virtually endless supply.<br>
<br>
All in all though, every charming class is taking a hit here.  Whether it's fair or not is another question, but it ain't just 'chanters. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showMessageRange?topicID=806.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showMessageRange?topicID=806.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showMessageRange?topicID=806.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showMessageRange?topicID=806.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showMessageRange?topicID=806.topic&start=101&stop=118>6</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showPrevMessage?topicID=806.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showNextMessage?topicID=806.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=806.topic&index=20><img src=http://quellious-collective.com/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=806.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.threadControl?topicID=806.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.subscribeUnregister